<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<XMLDialogs xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
    <Title>유니티를 사용하는데는 어떤 에디터가 좋나요?</Title>
    <SkipText>무슨 에디터가 좋냐에 대해 토론했지만, 결국엔 맞는걸 쓰는게 더 좋다는 걸 알았따.</SkipText>
    <Dialog>
        <BG Name="Black"/>
        <Text>
            <Text>유니티를 사용하는데는 어떤 에디터가 좋나요?</Text>
        </Text>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Bgm>School</Bgm>
        <BG Name="Class_Morning" Title="학교" Description="아침" Effect="FADE" Duration="2"/>
        <Text>
            <Name>{0}</Name>
            <Text>고민이네...</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" Clothes="Default" Face="Default" Pos="REND" Size="M" Dark="false"/>
        </Characters>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text Active="false">
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>뭐하고 있어?</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" Face="Default" Dark="false"/>
        </Characters>
        <Animations>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Move" Parameter="R2" Duration="2"/>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Bounce" Parameter="2" Duration="0.5"/>
            <Animation Type="UTIL" Effect="Wait" Duration="2"/>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Emotion" Parameter="Surprise" Duration="0.4"/>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Bounce" Parameter="1" Duration="0.2"/>
            <Animation Type="UTIL" Effect="Wait" Duration="1"/>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Move" Parameter="R1" Duration="1"/>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Scale" Parameter="L" Duration="1"/>
            <Animation Type="DIAL" Effect="On"/>
        </Animations>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>{0}</Name>
            <Text>아, 그냥 고민 중이였어.</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A"/>
        </Characters>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>무슨 고민?</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" Face="Default"/>
        </Characters>
        <Animations>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Emotion" Parameter="Question" Duration="1"/>
        </Animations>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>{0}</Name>
            <Text>원래 {Tip:Visual Studio}를 썼었는데, 친구가 {Tip:Visual Studio Code}를 계속 추천해서, 뭐가 더 낫나 싶어서</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A"/>
        </Characters>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>아, 에디터 관련 고민이구나?</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" Face="Smile"/>
        </Characters>
        <Animations>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Emotion" Parameter="Funny" Duration="1"/>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Bounce" Parameter="1" Duration="0.2"/>
        </Animations>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>나도 전부터 궁금했던 내용인데 같이 알아보면 되겠네.</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" Face="Default"/>
        </Characters>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>유명한 에디터는 3가지 정도가 있는거 같아</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" />
        </Characters>
        <Animations>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Move" Parameter="R3" Duration="1"/>
        </Animations>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>기본적인 에디터인 {Tip:Visual Studio}</Text>
        </Text>
        <Popup Name="VS">
            <Scale X="800px"/>
            <Pos X="-200" Y="140" />
        </Popup>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" />
        </Characters>
        <Animations>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Bounce" Parameter="2" Duration="0.2"/>
        </Animations>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>기본적인 만큼 다른 에디터에 비해 특출난 점은 없지만, 기본적인 만큼 성능은 보장되있지.</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" />
        </Characters>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>다음, {Tip:Visual Studio Code}</Text>
        </Text>
        <Popup Name="VSCode">
            <Scale X="800px"/>
            <Pos X="-200" Y="140" />
        </Popup>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" />
        </Characters>
        <Animations>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Bounce" Parameter="2" Duration="0.2"/>
        </Animations>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>나도 잘 안 써봐서 잘 모르겠는데, 다른 에디터보다 빠르고, 익스텐션이라 불리는 추가 기능을 장착할 수 있나봐.</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" />
        </Characters>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>마지막, {Tip:Rider}야, 내가 쓰고 있고, 장점을 말하자면 끝이 없지!</Text>
        </Text>
        <Popup Name="Rider">
            <Scale X="800px"/>
            <Pos X="-200" Y="140" />
        </Popup>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" Face="Smile"/>
        </Characters>
        <Animations>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Bounce" Parameter="2" Duration="0.2"/>
        </Animations>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>유니티와 다른 에디터보다 연동이 잘되있어 해당 스크립트를 사용하는 오브젝트를 탐색하거나 필드, 오브젝트 이름을 쉽게 검색하는 기능도 있고 깃과의 연동도 쉽게 되어서 간단하게 깃 내용도 확인할 수 있으며{Anim:SKIP}</Text>
        </Text>
        <Popup Name="Rider">
            <Scale X="800px"/>
            <Pos X="-200" Y="140" />
        </Popup>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" />
        </Characters>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text Active="false">
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>여러가지 쓸모가 많은 기능이 많은 대신, 메모리를 많이 먹는 단점이 있지.</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" Face="SmileFlush" Dark="false"/>
        </Characters>
        <Animations>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Bounce" Parameter="1" Duration="0.2"/>
            <Animation Type="UTIL" Effect="Wait" Duration="1"/>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Emotion" Parameter="Flush" Duration="1"/>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Shake" Parameter="-1" Duration="0.4"/>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Face" Parameter="SideFlush" Duration="0.4"/>
            <Animation Type="UTIL" Effect="Wait" Duration="1"/>
            <Animation Type="DIAL" Effect="On"/>
        </Animations>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text Active="false">
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>여러가지 에디터에 대해 들어봤는데, 어떤게 제일 좋다 생각해?</Text>
        </Text>
        <Option Script="Visual Studio" />
        <Option Script="Visual Studio Code" />
        <Option Script="Rider" />
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" Face="Default" Dark="false"/>
        </Characters>
        <Animations>
            <Animation Type="CHAR" Name="A" Effect="Move" Parameter="C" Duration="1"/>
            <Animation Type="UTIL" Effect="Wait" Duration="1"/>
            <Animation Type="DIAL" Effect="On"/>
        </Animations>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text Active="false">
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>확실히 그거도 좋긴한데, 다른 에디터들의 장점도 무시하긴 힘들다고 생각해.</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" Dark="false"/>
        </Characters>
        <Animations>
            <Animation Type="UTIL" Effect="Wait" Duration="1"/>
            <Animation Type="DIAL" Effect="On"/>
        </Animations>
    </Dialog>
    <Dialog>
        <Text>
            <Name>에이</Name>
            <Text>중요한건! 상황이랑 자신에 맞는 에디터를 쓰는게 중요하다는 것!</Text>
        </Text>
        <Characters>
            <Character Name="A" Face="SmileFlush"/>
        </Characters>
    </Dialog>
</XMLDialogs>